                <TextBlock Text="å¤åˆ¶ä¸€äº›å†…å®¹è¯•è¯•å§ï¼ˆæ”¯æŒæ–‡æœ¬ã€å›¾ç‰‡ã€æ–‡ä»¶ï¼‰" FontSize="12" Margin="0,4,0,0" Foreground="{DynamicResource TextDim}" HorizontalAlignment="Center"/>
            </StackPanel>

            <Border Grid.Row="4" Background="{DynamicResource BgCard}" CornerRadius="0,0,10,10" Padding="14,6">
                <Grid>
                    <TextBlock x:Name="TxtStatus" Text="å°±ç»ª" FontSize="11" Foreground="{DynamicResource TextDim}" VerticalAlignment="Center"/>
                    <TextBlock x:Name="TxtCount" Text="å…± 0 æ¡" FontSize="11" Foreground="{DynamicResource TextDim}" HorizontalAlignment="Right" VerticalAlignment="Center"/>
                </Grid>
            </Border>
        </Grid>
    </Border>
